Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.12,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly two years have passed\Nsince the terrible war
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.55,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,between the Zentradi and\Nthe Earth UN Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:57.70,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(82,140)}MY ALBUM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.29,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the Earth has been devastated,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:03.90,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,with the only survivors being\Nthose aboard the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.91,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,a handful of civilians on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:11.87,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and a few members of the Zentradi army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leader, please come in. Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our squad leader isn't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.74,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably out of his Valkyrie\Nand poking around the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:24.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a waste of time.\NThere aren't any survivors out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:29.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Having to fly this patrol every day\Nis a waste of time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the Zentradi have started running wild\Nin town so it's not like we have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a mission\Nand get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe those guys are just fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction was the only thing they lived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then we go and tell them they\Nhave to build things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotta be tough on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them are bound to get fed up\nbecause they can't adjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what makes 'em go and\Nstir up trouble with us humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's take our time doing our rounds\Nand hope nothing comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.33,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.20,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should start charging him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.46,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wouldn't work. He doesn't ask me,\nI just do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some things never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.05,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, I'm still in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.97,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"What's the matter, Hikaru?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.44,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Wipe that pitiful look off your face!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.20,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"You signed up because you wanted\Nto protect Minmay, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.03,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"What's she up to now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.27,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.57,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen her in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.94,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"You haven't even seen her?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:21.11,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"What, you got yourself\nanother woman, did you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.88,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wish I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.78,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Is that true, Hikaru?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.68,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The reason I joined the military\Nwas that I love women."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.13,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Protecting the woman you love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.74,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Is that a great job or what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect the woman you love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"A great job..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The woman I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.74,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The woman I love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.30,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.01,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Four, three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.36,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:24.53,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My body floats up and I fly away on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:27.02,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's on tour, going from city to city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.69,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People of Grante City, thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:36.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grante? That's near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:41.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's because of your hard work that\Nday by day, this city is being rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Minmay has come here today\Nto cheer on people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she'll continue to sing\Nher songs for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:55.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not for those unforgivable fools in the military\Nwho've made such a mess of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:01.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must rebuild our cities without\Ndelay and become self-sufficient
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:08.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means refusing those degrading\N"supplies" doled out by the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And now, let Minmay's singing embody\Nour hopes for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:18.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,as we present her next song,\N"Silver Moon, Red Moon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:26.30,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On the cafe terrace, dyed crimson with the sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.96,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fragrance of Turkish coffee fills the air
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:35.55,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Along with a listless tango rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:40.02,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone and lonely, but if I dance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:44.90,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze will blow through my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so she's at a city near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.48,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leader, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:48.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"What's up"?! What have you been\Ndoing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've been calling you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:59.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, but if you're going to leave your Valkyrie\Nplease take your radio with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.34,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. But listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are dandelions blooming\Nin the Red Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Out there in the wild?\NCome on, stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See?\NYou couldn't ask for better proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This whole area's outside the Nature\NReclamation Project zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm astonished, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw green from up in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seeds from the Nature Reclamation Project\Nmust have blown out and taken root.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:31.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, sorry about this but you all keep\Nflying patrol along your assigned course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Grante City for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you soon.\NCall me if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll take the radio\Nwith me if I leave my plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:51.25,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alone and lonely on Sunset Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:58.00,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sea breeze dies down, it's twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:05.98,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My bare feet still feel hot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:13.21,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving up on that flighty boy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:21.09,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm waiting for you, the dreamy one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:29.23,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming on Sunset Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He just can't get Minmay\Nout of his head, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When he's home, he's always looking\Nat pictures and posters of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.57,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he's head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:14.02,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For his plane instead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this really takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bring us a couple of beers, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.11,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:24.91,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This damn town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:43.94,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:51.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look! All those people there\Nand this is what we get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have been fine not getting anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pro!\NYou don't sing for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who told me to sing\Nto "keep everyone's spirits high"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.61,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange. It's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:13.61,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's for our livelihood. What's\nwrong with being compensated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:18.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Other people have it tough\Njust trying to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be thankful, even for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Thankful"? I'm supposed to be thankful\Nfor the military's handouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The people here may have given us this,\Nbut it all came from the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.\NThis piss-ant town is depressing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we're never going to\NMacross City, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop moping and making\Nthe military out to be evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you defending them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I don't know\nyou anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People who just drink and complain\Nare the absolute worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you say, Hikaru\Nand the rest of the military
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,deserve a lot more praise\Nthan you, the way you're acting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Praise"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're working hard to make the\NEarth the way it used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And who do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is responsible for the Earth\Nbeing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to clean up their mess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we should go our\Nseparate ways for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Macross City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? That's more than 5,000\Nkilometers away! How will you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of something.\NJust leave me alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:49.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Head for Vion City in the\NDanube Area at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's another fight or a robbery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some Zentradi have stolen weapons and are\Nattacking the human residential area!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've stolen weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Three battle pods.\NThat's all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll be there soon.\NWhat about my team?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've already contacted them.\NThey're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:10.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:29.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Major, I'm sorry to call you on your day off but\Nplease report to the command center at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some Zentradi have stolen weapons\Nand are on the rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fill me in once I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's our Leader?\NIsn't he here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's on his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to draw them away from the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:15.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of flight leader goes off\Nand ignores his own mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NThey called you in on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just went to see someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought things would escalate to the\Npoint where they'd run off with weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea who that "someone" was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:35.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who puts personal affairs before\Nhis mission isn't cut out to be a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:48.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the same way if I got\Ncalled in on my day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:01.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you think only\NVanessa got promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.83,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were wondering about that too?\NNo {\i1}waaay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Putting you aside for the moment,\NI've got more brains, personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and way more looks than her, so why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I withdraw the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work!\NWork!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Major's right there and\Nshe looks pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is our Leader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leader, you're really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, people. I'll take it\Nfrom here, so just fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your attack immediately and\Nthrow down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're unhappy about something,\Nwe'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, cease your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That look says you want to remind me\NI'm not cut out to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting weird back there, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Commander-in-Chief Global\nsays he wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Global?\NI wonder if it's about this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you get to see Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:28.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she and her manager Kaifun\Nare in Grante City now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her but I didn't talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just watched her from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem like the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:38.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:46.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:57.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo reporting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:07.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've received a thorough report\Nfrom Major Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that what we've\Nfeared has come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:18.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hoped this would be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:21.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be seeing more such incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:23.34,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:26.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that this same sort of\Ndisturbance will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:30.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I think it would be\Nwise to immediately transfer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:36.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,any Zentradi assigned to patrol units to other\Nposts such as duties inside the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:39.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right. I have several\NZentradi on my own squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If this happens again, Zentradi may\Nend up killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Then we'll transfer the Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:56.38,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I quietly stole away from your empty room
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:23:02.73,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to a train station, with no destination
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:08.57,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I finally understood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:19.35,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your tenderness is the reverse of your weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:12.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're not getting along?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:17.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't like that when\NI saw them a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:25.22,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and I've changed too much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:31.31,songM2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this is farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.43,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,108)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.43,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(301,452)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:40.17,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The acts of violence have become\Nmore frequent and widespread
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:44.30,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and have finally reached Macross City, where\Nthey show every sign of growing in scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:51.33,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the results of Exsedol's\Ninvestigation into humans and Zentradi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:54.18,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,hint at a dreadful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.74,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.95,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"LONELY SONG"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:00.24,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(91,140)}LONELY SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:23.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:29.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:36.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.75,0:24:44.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:51.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:56.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:15.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
